%section#wedding-details.page__section.section__wedding-details
  .row
    .small-12.columns
      %h4.section-title Wedding Details
  .row
    .small-12.columns
      .responsive-iframe-container
        :erb
          <iframe width='100%' height='500px' frameBorder='0' src='https://a.tiles.mapbox.com/v4/ttimsmith.lcej9aip/attribution,zoompan,geocoder.html?access_token=pk.eyJ1IjoidHRpbXNtaXRoIiwiYSI6Imh3Z0piYTAifQ.smU_4_vde53ZOKHrrDzpeA'></iframe>
  .row.row__details
    .small-12.medium-6.large-5.large-offset-1.columns
      %h4 Ceremony
      %p
        The wedding ceremony begins at 4 PM at the Kingdom Hall of Jehovah’s Witness in West Saint Paul. The address is:
      %p.adr
        %strong
          %span.street-address 1545 Christensen Ave,
          %span.region W. St. Paul, MN
          %span.postal-code 55118.


    .small-12.medium-6.large-5.columns.end
      %h4 Reception
      %p
        The reception is located at the beautiful Dakota Lodge in Thompson Park. You can arrive at the reception hall immediately after the wedding talk, and prayer for the feast will be at 5:30 PM. The address is:
      %p.adr
        %strong
          %span.street-address 1200 Stassen Ln,
          %span.region W. St. Paul, MN
          %span.postal-code 55118.

    .small-12.medium-12.large-10.large-offset-1.columns
      %hr/

    .small-12.medium-6.large-5.large-offset-1.columns
      %h4 Airport
      %p If you’re flying in from out of town, you’ll want to fly into the Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport (Airport code: MSP).

    .small-12.medium-6.large-5.columns.end
      %h4 Accommodations
      %p We’ve reserved a block of rooms at the [insert fancy hotel here]. It’s close to all the activity that’ll be going on that week.

    .small-12.medium-6.large-5.large-offset-1.columns
      %h4 Weather
      %p Trying to predict Minnesota weather is about as hard as keeping your eyes open when you sneeze. However, normally you can expect 50’s or 60’s in the spring. A sweater or light jacket would be a good idea.

    .small-12.medium-6.large-5.columns.end
      %h4 Other
      %p If you have any questions about anything, feel free to email us at #{mail_to "hello@timandkelbel.com", 'hello@timandkelbel.com', subject: "[timandkelbel.com] Question"}.

